{"tid":960820,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個好笑搭枱經歷","createTime":"2018-12-29T16:50:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-30T05:13:24.000Z","uid":60207,"like":7,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"e34f58ee96553f9a96dc703bf6c54bcb8a183522","tid":960820,"uid":60207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T16:50:33.000Z","msg":"話說上個禮拜同屋企人去大排檔食飯 我地7.30去要同人搭枱 對面係對情侶嚟 我同我家姐阿媽去食 咁食食下中途 聽到對面個男仔同個女仔講: 我岩岩先發現你係用左手食飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 之後個女仔望一望我地 再望一望個男仔 之後話:咩啊 我地全部都用左手架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 之後我地望住大家 笑左好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c892c31f67f54d86e8dffb44ae052f4e0202614","tid":960820,"uid":45772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T16:53:08.000Z","msg":"嗯"},{"pid":"4206e76e9e7236c588e56523f2915b24135f41d8","tid":960820,"uid":10277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T16:54:24.000Z","msg":"，。"},{"pid":"9a20051f0c5c00da6bd6c875ca544210da6ea40f","tid":960820,"uid":68641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T16:56:17.000Z","msg":"閱"},{"pid":"2a94dae89a2f9b343358599608766081b0028e0d","tid":960820,"uid":201155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T16:57:00.000Z","msg":"試過一張四人枱 三個人(包括我)都唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲記得係食緊阿原來了<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f17d7b1c5afd35eaa9d2e8633271322bf21e8916","tid":960820,"uid":88342,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T16:59:38.000Z","msg":"閱"},{"pid":"d7aef803a5fb6e08c3200ab8cab7b9b127691030","tid":960820,"uid":228266,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T16:59:39.000Z","msg":"試過一次搭枱，有條仔無啦啦勁大聲講：「阿